item.description:

oh and for the if statement not being closed, i know how to close but where would i close it?

You have to add a closing bracket( } ).

if(c.donator > 0 || c.playerRights >= 1){
c.triggerTele(1860, 5354, 0);
c.killMyNPCs();
c.resetfollowers();                         
} else {
//rest of code

That’s wrong, this would be right

if(c.donator > 0 || c.playerRights >= 1) {
   c.triggerTele(1860, 5354, 0);
   c.killMyNPCs();
   c.resetfollowers();                         
} else {
    //rest of code
}
